title: Ep - 82 - DAVID TOBOROWSKY FROM 90 DAY FIANCE
description:
An interview David Toborowsky from 90 Day Fiancé about how he was cast for the show, filming the season, his marriage to Annie, and his relationship with his friend Chris and his wife Nicki today.


Kate’s old college roommate Maura helps discuss the TLC show A Wedding Story and how it is the sole reason Kate got married and subsequently divorced at age 23. 


Comedy writer and podcast host Elizabeth Laime helps review an episode of My Five Wives on TLC, which documents the life of a polygamist family including patriarch Brady Williams, his five wives, and their 25 children.
